WEBVTT

00:00:01.851 --> 00:00:05.889 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s meet a sister who’s applied the counsel

00:00:05.889 --> 00:00:08.425 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to serve God from her youth on.

00:00:08.425 --> 00:00:11.961 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Sister Lillian Barnes is from Jamaica.

00:00:11.961 --> 00:00:15.799 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Her gifts to Jehovah
may have changed with age,

00:00:15.799 --> 00:00:18.234 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but what she gives to him today

00:00:18.234 --> 00:00:21.805 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is in no way less valuable.

00:04:41.564 --> 00:04:44.834 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
“Remember, then, your Grand Creator

00:04:44.834 --> 00:04:47.036 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
in the days of your youth.”

00:04:47.036 --> 00:04:49.906 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
That was Sister Barnes’ determination.

00:04:49.906 --> 00:04:52.642 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Lillian is now 108 years old

00:04:52.642 --> 00:04:56.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and has been baptized for nearly 82 years.

00:04:56.479 --> 00:05:00.550 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Her beautiful example shows the contentment

00:05:00.550 --> 00:05:05.054 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that comes from serving God
whole-souled at any age.

